    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《滑动英雄》是一款探索解谜游戏，在游戏中，你可以朝一个方向滑动，直到遇到障碍物为止。<br> <br>您能否战胜别墅的重重考验，揭开您被监禁的真相？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003410/extras/d7a7d03ffcb2686e05d618ea72db34c2.poster.avif?t=1755241826\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003410/extras/d7a7d03ffcb2686e05d618ea72db34c2.webm?t=1755241826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003410/extras/d7a7d03ffcb2686e05d618ea72db34c2.mp4?t=1755241826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003410/extras/b81ecbe552a7a9fc43897fa0aeac54cb.poster.avif?t=1755241826\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003410/extras/b81ecbe552a7a9fc43897fa0aeac54cb.webm?t=1755241826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003410/extras/b81ecbe552a7a9fc43897fa0aeac54cb.mp4?t=1755241826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一款充满动感和神秘色彩的 Metroidvania 游戏！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被囚禁在一座阴森的威尼斯别墅中，<strong>运用您的智慧帮助威尼斯军人卢卡·西科莫罗</strong>逃离这里。<strong>在Sliding Hero中</strong>，每次移动都是对策略的考验，因为<strong>您只能朝一个方向滑动</strong>直到碰到障碍物 — <strong>将移动本身变成一个谜题</strong>。探索一个黑暗而错综复杂的世界，灵感来自<strong>18 世纪的威尼斯和狂欢节的神秘蒙面</strong>，危险和欺骗潜伏在每个阴影中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003410/extras/62f46ac7a2a0bbdd90eb7485a8dfcc39.poster.avif?t=1755241826\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003410/extras/62f46ac7a2a0bbdd90eb7485a8dfcc39.webm?t=1755241826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003410/extras/62f46ac7a2a0bbdd90eb7485a8dfcc39.mp4?t=1755241826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>掌握滑动的技巧</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用危险环境、武器、文物和你自己的冲力来<strong>消灭敌人并避开致命陷阱</strong>。每次遇险都是对技能的考验，<strong>解谜和战斗无缝衔接</strong>在一个易于学习、但难以掌握的移动系统中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003410/extras/d1082e849fb42d3b7e84cbe73ebebf30.poster.avif?t=1755241826\" width=800 height=474 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003410/extras/d1082e849fb42d3b7e84cbe73ebebf30.webm?t=1755241826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003410/extras/d1082e849fb42d3b7e84cbe73ebebf30.mp4?t=1755241826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003410/extras/81cd4c6a55cc512907a9fd212fc73bc7.poster.avif?t=1755241826\" width=800 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003410/extras/81cd4c6a55cc512907a9fd212fc73bc7.webm?t=1755241826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003410/extras/81cd4c6a55cc512907a9fd212fc73bc7.mp4?t=1755241826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索互相连接的世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >别墅是一个<strong>充满隐藏通道、上锁的门的地方，然后秘密</strong>等待被揭开。<strong>解锁新工具</strong>让您<strong>到达</strong>之前无法企及的区域，<strong>打造捷径</strong>，并与居住在其中<strong>古怪而神秘的人物</strong>互动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003410/extras/d8db961764a2390b566b5f5675272e78.poster.avif?t=1755241826\" width=800 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003410/extras/d8db961764a2390b566b5f5675272e78.webm?t=1755241826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003410/extras/d8db961764a2390b566b5f5675272e78.mp4?t=1755241826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>黑暗的威尼斯之梦</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >走进一个精美的像素图像艺术世界，沉浸<strong>在威尼斯狂欢节的优雅与不安中</strong>。令人难忘的原创配乐，灵感来自<strong>意大利巴洛克风格旋律</strong>增添了游戏氛围，让您<strong>拼凑出一个充满神秘、宿命和自我发现的故事</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003410/extras/8b66022ca9eaeb03dd0e17ffb13478b2.poster.avif?t=1755241826\" width=800 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003410/extras/8b66022ca9eaeb03dd0e17ffb13478b2.webm?t=1755241826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003410/extras/8b66022ca9eaeb03dd0e17ffb13478b2.mp4?t=1755241826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独特的解谜战斗系统</strong>围绕基于动量的运动来构建。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多种武器可供解锁</strong>，每种武器都有特定的谜题机制</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>氛围浓厚的威尼斯场景</strong>，将历史之美与怪诞幻想融为一体。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>非线性银河恶魔城探索</strong>— 发现新能力，开辟新道路。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>引人入胜且精心设计的Boss战</strong>，策略是关键。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>快节奏的移动系统</strong>专为快速奔跑而设计。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
